Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.29,0:00:06.27,Default,Flashback,0000,0000,0000,,I'll rip you apart with my fangs, Earth Engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.45,Default,Flashback,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.84,0:00:13.90,Default,Flashback,0000,0000,0000,,A planetary sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:25.29,Default,Flashback,0000,0000,0000,,Albion!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.46,0:00:38.55,Default,Flashback,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:45.64,Default,Flashback,0000,0000,0000,,Albion... What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:18.97,Default,Flashback,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Albion appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it interfered with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something bad is about to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:16.55,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Assault of the Planetary Gear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:32.76,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Having a summer break like this is a nice change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.92,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Pitz.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:40.41,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Want a watermelon seed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:47.28,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're too worried about Hana to eat, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.49,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Daichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:54.80,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about Hana...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:57.55,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,But what about Teppei? Will he be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:01.92,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It won't do any good for you to get depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.35,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:13.26,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Belly Button...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.63,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Belly Button Forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:22.30,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Well? What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:24.78,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do I think? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:32.24,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is the beautiful, beautiful Akari-chan \Nshowing you her belly button
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:35.62,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,as a magic spell to make you feel better!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:37.54,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Belly Button Forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:41.36,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,See? You feel better, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:44.91,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... A little, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:46.64,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:49.72,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's bust our way in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:56.31,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Last night's earthquake was caused by \Nmovement of the ship on the sea floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:05:00.00,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,We believe she used her own body \Nas an energy relay circuit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:03.86,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,to activate Machine Goodfellow \NAramusha's main systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:09.33,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,We know she has an unknown type of organelle
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:13.39,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,in her body that we Homo sapiens don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:16.48,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Our hypothesis is that the energy she used
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:21.09,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,is a variant of the Orgone energy \Nthat is stored on the Blume.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:29.80,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,These are the results of the mental \Nhealth test, the forensic psychiatry test,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:32.97,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,and the thought examination system \Nthat we conducted this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:36.71,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,He was very cooperative with all the tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:44.61,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Teppei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:48.86,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,That Machine Goodfellow you used last night
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:54.45,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,was secretly taken from Macbeth Enterprises \Nduring the Kanda incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:56.66,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time as you, in fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:06:02.13,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,We knew it was able to recognize you specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:06.57,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,That's your own personal \NNeural Maneuver System.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:09.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.89,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Until yesterday, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.79,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Macbeth Enterprises
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:21.35,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,ostensibly developed it as a man-machine interface
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:27.61,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,for the latest mobile weaponry, but early on, \Nwe realized that it had a greater function...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:36.20,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,No, that it had been developed for \Nan entirely different purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:41.33,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,But we didn't know what it was for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:45.23,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Were you controlling that Kiltgang Type-3
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:48.54,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,that appeared in the Earth Engine's combat zone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:53.76,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think you were controlling it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:07:00.83,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}were{\i0} that Type-3, which is \Nstill floating in Alpha sector.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:03.27,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:08.89,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you... That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:16.41,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,He was the Kiltgang itself? \NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:19.61,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Until yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:24.76,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei had the mentality of a 17-year-old \Nboy who was born and raised in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:29.04,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at him, I never doubted that for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:31.68,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,But what about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:36.70,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be very interested to learn about \Nhis memories and consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.37,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,now that he's become a Kiltgang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.64,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,This fact constitutes a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:45.36,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,It is of grave significance in determining \Nthe course of the battle from here on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:47.90,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:56.12,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Until we have more information, \Nthis matter is classified top-secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.20,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That goes for HQ, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:04.25,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you realize that decision is outside
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:06.70,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,your authority to make, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:10.46,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,To me, the most important fact is that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:15.48,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei's Kiltgang saved the Earth Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.41,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't going to the base?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:00.39,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,First, we need to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:02.57,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You just ate that watermelon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:04.45,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.45,0:09:07.07,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,How about a crêpe? They're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.49,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:12.38,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll take a banana crêpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:14.07,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a mango crêpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:15.88,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Coming right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:23.64,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Your belly button won't become magical \Nif you show it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:26.67,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe it will?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:28.50,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:29.81,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:33.09,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Want some, Pitz?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:34.75,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:35.67,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:39.94,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:42.27,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't waste food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:43.35,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:46.24,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,That's a big trailer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:49.48,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I travel around Japan selling crêpes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.89,0:09:52.26,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Today's my first time on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:55.90,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,The wind feels good here, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:58.11,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,The wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:00.90,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:14.03,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Can we come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:15.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Just a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:27.77,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you can enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:30.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Those look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:31.85,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,They are good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:36.53,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Hana's undergoing a physical \Nexam at the medical center.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:38.90,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Teppei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:43.08,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Room 45, in block C.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:44.70,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's the interrogation room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:47.86,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Stop touching things without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:49.33,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that place...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:52.39,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:01.39,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Fine... Go and see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:09.23,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you being a bit soft?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:48.10,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid, I was kind of proud of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:53.96,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But once I realized how strange being able to \Nmake a rainbow appear over my hand was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.11,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I avoided doing it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:12:00.57,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I pretended I couldn't do it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:04.10,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I often dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:08.94,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,but when I'm awake, it feels more like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:16.42,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow I knew that the real me \Nwasn't the person I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:20.17,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,But you're you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:24.86,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:28.35,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You really surprised me this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:54.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I heard your crêpes are really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:58.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't enter without permission... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:00.59,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You can't give us permission yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:03.05,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we'll just go in ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:07.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't change the base's security measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:11.06,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you can't fool a machine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:14.83,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If you go in, something scary will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:18.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wouldn't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:21.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:23.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:28.20,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to fool machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:34.50,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:41.84,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,My cute little bunny has taken \Nover their defense system.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:56.52,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:02.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:04.07,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:11.95,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The base's antipersonnel fortress \Nsystem has been shut off...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:12.85,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:17.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Something's happening in block C!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.14,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,They're after Teppei?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:21.75,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Rita, Thunder... Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:36.22,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,A direct attack on HQ itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:39.13,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Salty Dog? The Ark Faction, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:43.39,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't told HQ about Teppei yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:45.82,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,If they're after Teppei, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:49.45,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:18.48,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,You're Alaya, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:22.77,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No... I don't use that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:25.56,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,Well, your avatar name doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:27.26,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,You're Albion, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.26,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,His memories haven't returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:31.07,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:33.50,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,He abreacted into the Kiltgang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:34.45,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:38.16,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:40.80,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,I was really worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:43.75,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you interfere yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.28,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a traitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.05,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:52.22,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:55.18,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:57.53,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Daichi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:58.81,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:15:59.93,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:02.31,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Throw down your weapons and surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.87,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're outnumbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:07.27,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not waste food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:09.06,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:13.49,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,These guys' libidos will eventually feed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:15.20,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:22.87,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:25.50,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Good, he's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:27.46,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Then, are you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.67,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:35.97,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,The crêpe seller, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:40.35,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Planetary Gear Amarok.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:44.56,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm the Planetary Gear Malkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:51.74,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Do you regard Earth's humans as food?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:55.53,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:59.24,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,But that's what the people of this world want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:04.01,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not waste food,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:07.46,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,but if you want to fight, I won't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.46,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Logical, logical...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.39,0:17:15.72,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful. The antipersonnel fortress \Nsystem is coming on line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:20.06,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Logical, logical! Bye-bye, naughty rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:22.14,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.14,0:17:30.15,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:34.32,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,She deactivated my rabbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.28,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,This really is a bit scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:38.74,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's run like rabbits!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:40.33,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:42.45,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:29.12,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:36.55,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,A mobile weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:39.76,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wreak some havoc, Tenrohsei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:51.02,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's their mobile weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:09.37,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.24,0:19:16.21,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,Albion...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:18.97,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Stop doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:21.72,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's me you want, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:26.43,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,If you come with us, \Nwe won't hurt any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:30.11,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,Not that they'll survive long either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:37.47,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:40.70,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, pretty boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.71,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying too hard to look tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:48.70,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You belong here, with all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:52.71,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:56.00,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you can do here, Earthling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:57.92,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:02.59,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:07.96,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei is one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:12.31,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,Neoteny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:20.32,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you have Teppei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:36.92,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,Moco, he got me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:46.89,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:59.38,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen that Livlaster before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:01.28,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't the one from the Blume.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:03.86,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,It may have materialized here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:06.70,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,That'd make it the Livlaster Tanegashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:11.04,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't believe a neoteny appeared \Nfrom one of the Earthlings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:14.91,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Albion really does want to betray us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.91,0:21:17.67,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:20.62,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling of being a Kiltgang...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:24.26,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's a sense of pleasure he can never give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:36.14,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,They're a terrifying opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:39.36,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,They looked like young children.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:42.59,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Are they the enemies we're fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:44.74,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how they look,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:49.20,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,if their Kiltgangs reach Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:51.48,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,we lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.71,0:21:55.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:21:57.67,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Akari-san's amazing, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:22:01.63,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one who brought our \Ndefense system back on line.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:03.01,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.79,0:22:05.05,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,So, where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:08.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was tired and going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:11.64,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Akari Yomatsuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:13.89,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei Arashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:15.55,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hana Mutou.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:18.52,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,And Daichi Manatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.11,0:22:21.27,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Science Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:23.08,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.52,0:22:26.62,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,When you look at them, don't you feel something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.96,0:22:29.06,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Feel something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.94,0:22:35.51,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,All I can say is that I have no logical proof of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.07,0:22:39.25,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,You want to feel something, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.91,0:22:41.90,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,You want to feel that something in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.24,0:24:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kivotos Plan team is in artificial sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aboard the Globe Orbital Base {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.78,0:24:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them, the person who \Ngave Teppei their genes,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.71,0:24:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is targeted by strange enemy spies.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.62,0:24:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei decides to...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.84,0:24:32.49,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on episode 5 of {\i1}Captain Earth{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.49,0:24:34.23,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Starry Sky's Picture Book.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.49,0:24:34.91,Title2,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Starry Sky's Picture Book
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.91,0:24:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Engine, expand!
